Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=14}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 5,0:02:12.65,0:02:16.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who was the first to find him?\NPlease let us question them! - OG}Quem o encontrou primeiro?\NPor favor, deixem a gente interrogá-los!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.60,0:02:18.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who's the culprit?! - OG}Há algum suspeito?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are they connected with\Nthe annihilation of Franky House?! - OG}{Did they destroy Franky House? - JT}Alguma conexão com a destruição da Franky House?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:21.58,0:02:22.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Please give us a statement! - OG}{Do you have a statement?! - JT}Podemos ter uma declaração?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.80,0:02:24.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Please tell us the latest developments! - OG}{Are there any developments?! - JT}Alguma novidade?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, did you hear about the incident\Nat Shipyard Island? - OG}Ei, você ouviu sobre o que\Naconteceu na Ilha do Estaleiro?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:27.72,0:02:29.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is it true that he died? - OG}Ele realmente morreu?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It must be Franky who did it! - OG}O Franky deve ter feito isso!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.56,0:02:34.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This happened because they left him at large! - OG}{This happened because\Nthey let him have free rein! - JT}Isso aconteceu porque não prendem ele!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:34.47,0:02:38.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, there's also a strong chance it was\Ndone by pirates who visit the shipyard. - OG}{Well, it could very well be\Nthat those pirates at the shipyard did it. - JT}Bom, também pode ter sido algum\Ndos piratas que visitam o estaleiro.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então é aqui que vocês estavam.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.18,0:02:54.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We went to the trouble of getting a room\Nat this inn and yet no one's in there. - OG}A gente se deu ao trabalho de pegar um quarto,\Nmas ninguém tá usando.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.63,0:02:57.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I guess you all couldn't sleep, huh? - OG}Acho que ninguém conseguiu dormir, né?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cadê o Luffy?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ali.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde você foi, Sanji?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:11.32,0:03:18.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hmm... I kept a lookout at the rocky cape all night,\Nthinking that Robin-chan might come back. - OG}Hm? Fiquei vigiando no cabo rochoso\Na noite toda caso a Robin voltasse.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.60,0:03:28.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wonder where she went... without saying anything to us... - OG}Pra onde será que ela foi...\NSem nem falar nada pra gente.{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.19,0:03:37.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acho que vou andar\Npela cidade procurando ela hoje.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.04,0:03:41.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wonder if we can find her. - OG}Será que vamos encontrá-la?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.08,0:03:43.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem sabe?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é como se eu tivesse\Nlugares específicos em mente,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.24,0:03:50.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but in any case, it's certain that she's somewhere in this town. - OG}mas de qualquer forma,\Nela tem que estar em algum lugar aqui.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.12,0:03:55.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's make this inn the place to meet up if something happens. - OG}{Let's make this inn our meeting place if something happens. - JT}Se algo acontecer,\Na gente se encontra aqui na pousada.{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll go look for her, too. - OG}Eu também vou ajudar a procurar.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.59,0:03:59.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza. Então vamos.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.72,0:04:03.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami{-san}!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is terrible! - OG}Tenho más notícias.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:04.51,0:04:07.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A cidade inteira tá falando sobre isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.52,0:04:12.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy! Last night, Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]\Nfrom the shipyard was... - OG}Luffy! Ontem à noite,\No Sr. Iceburg do estaleiro foi...{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.73,0:04:17.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]was shot in his home?! - OG}O Sr. Iceburg levou um tiro na casa dele?!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.74,0:04:19.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Don't be silly! - OG}{Hey! Don't joke around! - JT}Ei, para de besteira!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Was he killed?! - OG}{Is he dead?! - JT}Ele foi assassinado?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.94,0:04:21.78,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, hey!}{\i1}Calma aí!{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.78,0:04:26.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He isn't someone who makes enemies of people! - OG}Ele não é o tipo de pessoa que faz inimigos!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.29,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Espera! Se acalma, Paulie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:26.29,0:04:29.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Me escuta.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.00,0:04:35.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Look, Iceburg-san was found covered in blood\Nin his room this morning. - OG}Olha, o Sr. Iceburg foi encontrado\Ncoberto de sangue no quarto dele hoje de manhã.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.25,0:04:39.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He's still in a coma, so he's unconscious right now. - OG}Ele entrou em coma e ainda não acordou.{\i0}{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.26,0:04:42.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{In any case,\Ncome to the main office immediately! - OG}De qualquer forma, vem pro escritório agora!{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Lulu! Where's Paulie? - OG}Lulu! Viu o Paulie?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I just called him. He'll be here soon. - OG}Acabei de ligar pra ele. Ele chega logo.{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I see. - OG}Entendo.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.79,0:04:57.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Newspaper reporters are already here and it's quite an uproar outside... - OG}{Newspaper reporters are already here and there's an uproar outside... - JT}Os repórteres estão fazendo\Num baita alvoroço lá fora.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:57.40,0:05:02.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{even though we're the ones who want to know what's going on. - OG}Bem irônico, já que a gente tá\Ntão por fora quanto eles.{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:02.75,0:05:08.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Although they tore up the whole office, there's no trace of money or valuables being stolen. - OG}{\q2}Apesar de terem revirado o escritório todo, não há\Nsinal de dinheiro ou objetos de valor roubados.{JT/Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.49,0:05:14.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If it wasn't for robbery,\Nwho'd have a reason to shoot Iceburg-san? - OG}Se não foi roubo, por que alguém\Nentraria e daria um tiro no Sr. Iceburg?{JT}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De fato.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, isso é um desastre.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.54,0:05:21.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A cidade inteira está em pânico.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se algo acontecer com ele...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:24.60,0:05:29.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Galley-La Company, assim como\NWater Seven, estão acabadas.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.60,0:05:45.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Doutor... como ele está?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.00,0:05:57.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele levou dois tiros pela frente\Ne três pelas costas.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.88,0:06:02.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não sei o que aconteceu naquele\Nquarto ontem à noite, mas foi brutal.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.11,0:06:10.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Segundo a análise forense,\Nnenhuma fechadura do prédio foi arrombada.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.27,0:06:14.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O crime ocorreu em um quarto\Nonde ninguém poderia ter entrado.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.69,0:06:21.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A única coisa encontrada no quarto\Nfoi uma máscara comum.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.36,0:06:27.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? Icechefe?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.48,0:06:31.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Disseram que ele está inconsciente agora.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.04,0:06:35.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo gosta dele. Por quê...?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De quem a gente tá falando, Nami?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.32,0:06:40.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De alguém que nos ajudou ontem.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.42,0:06:43.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele administra a empresa de construção naval\Ne é prefeito de Water Seven.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.25,0:06:47.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece ser alguém importante.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:48.14,0:06:51.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra essa cidade, um incidente desse\Né o maior que pode acontecer.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou dar uma olhada.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.27,0:06:55.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera, Luffy! Eu vou junto!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.76,0:07:01.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, então vamos procurar a Robin.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:04.03,0:07:05.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E você?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.40,0:07:10.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou ficar observando mais um pouco.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Extra! Extra! Leiam tudo sobre isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.79,0:07:22.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O herói de Water Seven, nosso prefeito,\NIceburg, foi assassinado!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.81,0:07:24.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Temos todas as últimas notícias!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.47,0:07:28.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Prefeito Iceburg está bem?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.68,0:07:31.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é terrível.\NComo isso pôde acontecer com ele?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:31.18,0:07:35.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um ataque tão violento...\NPiratas devem ter feito isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espero que a gente pegue eles!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.94,0:07:41.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Também teve uns piratas que\Naprontaram no Dock One ontem.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:41.61,0:07:42.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gangue Mikazuki?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.92,0:07:47.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu suspeito que o governo pode estar envolvido.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lulu, como é?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.53,0:07:52.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tô falando do Corgi.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.07,0:07:58.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Toda vez que ele vem falar com\No Sr. Iceburg, é dispensado.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Franky deve ser o culpado, no final das contas.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.25,0:08:06.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't know what his deal was,\Nbut I think Corgi held some undue resentment. - OG}Não sei qual era o problema dele,\Nmas acho que o Corgi guardava um certo rancor.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.21,0:08:08.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não reclama do governo.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.34,0:08:11.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se alguém ouvir, vai te custar caro.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:13.10,0:08:17.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qual é o objetivo do criminoso?\NRiqueza ou poder?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.18,0:08:20.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem é esse assassino que\Ndesapareceu sem deixar rastro?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.19,0:08:26.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos fez isso?! Vão pagar!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por viajarem no Puffing Tom.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.86,0:08:39.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Em breve chegaremos à Blue Station\Nna Cidade da Água, Water Seven.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, Paulie!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.57,0:09:09.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Paulie! Pode nos dar uma declaração?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já te disseram alguma coisa?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.95,0:09:14.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca. Sai da minha frente.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:14.24,0:09:16.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que explicação a empresa te deu?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, diga alguma coisa!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.15,0:09:20.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês são surdos?! Eu disse pra sair da minha frente!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.75,0:09:25.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Sr. Iceburg está em algum tipo de problema\Nque pode colocar a vida dele em risco?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.17,0:09:26.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lembra de algo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.53,0:09:27.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Algum envolvimento com piratas?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.95,0:09:28.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Paulie! Nos diga–
Dialogue: 5,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu disse pra saírem da frente!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seus imbecis!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.30,0:09:38.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então ele realmente foi atacado.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.81,0:09:42.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É. Talvez a gente não consiga ver ele\Nmesmo indo ao estaleiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:42.73,0:09:45.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então vamos até a casa dele.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:45.42,0:09:48.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Disseram que a residência dele fica no escritório principal.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.40,0:09:52.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kiwi... Mozu...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.52,0:09:55.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu tô sonhando?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, Mano...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.33,0:10:02.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é, sem dúvida,\Nonde a Franky House ficava.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.91,0:10:05.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas isso é...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.84,0:10:07.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,...horrível.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.42,0:10:15.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que diabos aconteceu aqui?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.76,0:10:31.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem fez isso enquanto eu tava fora?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.57,0:10:35.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendo. Devem ser eles.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.82,0:10:39.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como ousa, Chapéu de Palha Luffy?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.88,0:10:43.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é vingança por termos roubado\Nos seus 200 milhões de berry?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.75,0:10:47.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como ousa fazer isso\Ncom meus preciosos subordinados?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tão cruel...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.92,0:10:53.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Imperdoável...!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mano Franky!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.59,0:10:56.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você voltou!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.88,0:10:57.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mano!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.68,0:11:01.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, vocês estão bem? Que bom.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.20,0:11:08.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Foi terrível. Aqueles caras eram insanos!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.40,0:11:13.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma,\Nvocê tem que fazê-los pagar,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.32,0:11:16.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,então estivemos monitorando\Nos movimentos dos Chapéus de Palha.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.15,0:11:18.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde eles estão?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.11,0:11:21.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente viu eles entrando numa pousada.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.20,0:11:24.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De lá, eles foram\Npra Ilha do Estaleiro há pouco.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.66,0:11:28.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Devem estar indo pro\NDock One, igual ontem.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza... Entendi!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.71,0:11:37.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha Luffy, essa vai ser\Na surra da sua vida!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.49,0:11:49.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vovó! Vovó!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.65,0:11:53.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O vento tá muito forte! Ei, Vovó!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.40,0:11:59.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vento louco! Vento louco! Vento louco!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.62,0:12:02.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Controla a empolgação.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.37,0:12:10.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's a southern wind... the caloque, huh? - OG}É um vento sul... o caloque, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:11.69,0:12:14.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As ondas também estão ficando agitadas.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.34,0:12:18.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nesse ritmo, o serviço do Sea Train\Nvai ter que ser suspenso hoje à noite.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.54,0:12:22.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chimney e Gonbe! Se preparem\Npra voltar pra ilha!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:22.62,0:12:23.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá bom!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.67,0:12:34.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Aqua Laguna está vindo.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:44.06,0:12:45.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Atenção, por favor.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.83,0:12:49.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqui é a Agência Meteorológica\Nde Water Seven.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.79,0:12:54.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um alerta de Aqua Laguna\Nacaba de ser emitido para toda a ilha.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:54.63,0:12:58.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estimamos que chegará\Na Water Seven depois da meia-noite de hoje.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.94,0:13:01.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é... É essa época do ano.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.44,0:13:04.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu estava preocupado\Ncom o incidente do Prefeito Iceburg.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:04.18,0:13:07.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! A Aqua Laguna está vindo!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.17,0:13:09.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Avisem a todos!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.27,0:13:11.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O trabalho acabou por hoje!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.73,0:13:12.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que tá acontecendo?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.84,0:13:14.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqua Laguna?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, com licença.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.44,0:13:19.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi aquele anúncio?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.35,0:13:21.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você não sabe? É–
Dialogue: 5,0:13:21.40,0:13:24.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, você é de fora?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:24.00,0:13:25.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Veio numa hora ruim.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.37,0:13:31.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqua Laguna é, basicamente, uma ressaca.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.58,0:13:32.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma ressaca, é?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.83,0:13:36.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo. Não esqueça\Nde evacuar pro terreno mais alto.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.40,0:13:38.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A cidade vai ficar submersa no mar.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.42,0:13:41.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A cidade vai ficar "submersa"...?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:42.68,0:13:45.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe. Não vai\Nacontecer agora.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A previsão disse que\Nchega por volta da meia-noite.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:47.68,0:13:51.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, isso acontece todo ano. Cuidado!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.18,0:13:52.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.35,0:13:55.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai ficar submersa no mar?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.20,0:13:58.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Esse lugar vai afundar?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.01,0:14:01.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece que sim. De qualquer forma,\Nvamos nos apressar e encontrar a Robin.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.64,0:14:02.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.78,0:14:04.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, nos digam algo!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.28,0:14:05.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sr. Iceburg!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que diabos aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.23,0:14:09.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que tá acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:10.24,0:14:12.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não dá pra entrar, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.44,0:14:16.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, a gente precisa\Nver o Icechefe de novo de algum jeito.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.87,0:14:20.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Com licença. Você sabe onde fica\Na entrada do escritório principal?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.76,0:14:22.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, isso não vai rolar.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.63,0:14:28.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dá pra entrar pelo Dock One, mas só\Npessoas envolvidas e certos repórteres podem.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.76,0:14:32.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo quer saber como ele está,\Nmas não podemos fazer nada.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendo... Obrigado.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.51,0:14:43.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que confusão é essa? Tá lotado.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.94,0:14:47.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, quanto maior a plateia, melhor.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! Essa batida...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser... Não ele!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.22,0:15:00.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que logo agora?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.71,0:15:04.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, vocês!\NAcabaram de chamar meu nome?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.67,0:15:07.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não chamamos! Vai embora!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.30,0:15:10.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde?! Onde ele está?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.38,0:15:13.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Ele tá ali!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.35,0:15:14.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tá aqui!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:14.73,0:15:17.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yow! Yow! Yow!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.23,0:15:22.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,♪ Vamos lá, não sejam tímidos,\Nperguntem meu nome! ♪
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.23,0:15:24.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não queremos perguntar! Cai fora!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você atacou o Prefeito Iceburg, não foi?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.61,0:15:29.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?! Ele fez isso?!\N– Deve ser ele!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.15,0:15:31.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sai dessa ilha!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.57,0:15:33.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você devia ser enforcado, moleque!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.62,0:15:37.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ugh... cala a boca, bando de moscas!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.12,0:15:42.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,♪ Eu sou o cara número um super dessa ilha! ♪
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,♪ O chefão do submundo de Water Seven! ♪
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.63,0:15:47.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,♪ Isso mesmo! As pessoas me chamam de... Uau! ♪
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.67,0:15:52.80,Main-207+,,0,0,15,,Franky!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.27,0:16:04.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aparece, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.21,0:16:09.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você deve estar aqui, Chapéu de Palha Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.23,0:16:13.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que isso?!\NAquele cara pervertido chamou meu nome!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.74,0:16:17.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As pessoas não chamaram ele de Franky agora?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:17.33,0:16:19.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É ele!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.66,0:16:24.12,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele é quem bateu no Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.12,0:16:28.09,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse dinheiro é nosso agora.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:39.10,0:16:41.14,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Devolve... isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.14,0:16:45.02,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Devolveeeeee!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É ele...!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.57,0:16:55.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, sunga de biquíni!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.49,0:16:55.53,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:59.10,0:17:00.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:03.58,0:17:05.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou o Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.38,0:17:10.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Não tem nenhuma informação? Ah, vamos...\N– O que tá acontecendo?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:10.46,0:17:11.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pessoal...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.02,0:17:16.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kalifa...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:20.64,0:17:24.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, entrem no quarto... em silêncio.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:24.31,0:17:26.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê...? Então...!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.85,0:17:29.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Sr. Iceburg...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.44,0:17:32.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,acabou de recobrar a consciência.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.07,0:17:36.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Que ótimo!\N– Que ótimo!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu podia pular de alegria!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sr. Iceburg!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.80,0:17:45.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, desculpa por preocupar vocês...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.25,0:17:48.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, que bom que está vivo!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, foque em descansar.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:50.67,0:17:53.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente cuida das coisas no estaleiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:53.76,0:17:59.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Preciso contar pra vocês... sobre os culpados\Nque invadiram meu quarto ontem à noite...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.39,0:18:02.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah... Ainda estão investigando.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, mas eu me lembro.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:04.43,0:18:05.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê...?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.41,0:18:06.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?\N– O quê?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.90,0:18:14.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eram dois. Um era\Num homem grande usando uma máscara.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:14.03,0:18:16.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O outro era...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.95,0:18:19.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,uma mulher alta com cabelo longo e preto.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:22.95,0:18:27.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não há como errar.\NAqueles olhos pretos pertencem à...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.21,0:18:38.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Prefeito Iceburg...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.09,0:18:43.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Prefeito Iceburg recobrou a consciência!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.56,0:18:44.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É verdade?!\N– Isso aí!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.97,0:18:47.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Ótimo!\N– Viva!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.44,0:18:57.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então você é o tal...\NChapéu de Palha Luffy?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.32,0:19:06.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você aprontou bastante\Nenquanto eu tava fora, hein?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:06.29,0:19:09.08,Main-207+,,0,0,15,,Quando voltei, não acreditei no que vi...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.08,0:19:14.17,Main-207+,,0,0,15,,Bom, minha casa tá completamente irreconhecível.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.17,0:19:18.47,Main-207+,,0,0,15,,E como ousa tratar\Nmeus subordinados tão cruelmente?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.05,0:19:21.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não aguento mais.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.39,0:19:24.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ninguém me segura essa semana!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.20,0:19:26.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nada que você diga vai importar.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:26.93,0:19:32.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só vou me acalmar quando te despedaçar!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:32.40,0:19:33.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, você!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:33.49,0:19:34.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.27,0:19:38.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, você! O que você fez\Ncom nossos 200 milhões de berry?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Devolve pra gente!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.61,0:19:43.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?! 200 milhões de berry?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:43.91,0:19:47.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já gastei tudo! Acabou!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:48.45,0:19:51.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês obviamente roubaram esse\Ndinheiro de alguém.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:51.26,0:19:55.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês não têm moral pra ficar\Nse achando, piratas!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tanto faz.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.13,0:19:56.59,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mentira! Dinheiro importa sim!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:58.96,0:20:01.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, eu não vou ficar feliz...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.10,0:20:04.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,até chutar seu traseiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.30,0:20:05.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:05.85,0:20:10.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, eu não vou ficar feliz, seu desgraçado!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Desce logo aqui!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.52,0:20:15.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! É isso! O Franky vai surtar!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.20,0:20:18.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Evacuem! Todo mundo, evacuem!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Saiam daqui!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que ele tá fazendo?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:55.21,0:20:57.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele cuspiu fogo pela boca!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:57.89,0:20:59.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que ele é?!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:01.67,0:21:04.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês nunca viram ninguém\Ncuspir fogo antes?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:04.95,0:21:07.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, ele pode ter poderes de Akuma no Mi.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, qual fruta?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:21.07,0:21:24.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que isso?! Ele pulou na água!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:24.31,0:21:28.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele é burro? Se comeu uma Akuma no Mi, vai se afogar!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:28.68,0:21:32.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele deve ter escorregado e caído!\NEle definitivamente tem poder de cuspir fogo.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:47.41,0:21:50.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que isso?! Ele sabe nadar?!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:50.83,0:21:52.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:52.37,0:21:56.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não comi nenhuma Akuma no Mi!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:01.00,0:22:02.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:03.61,0:22:06.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu ouvi sobre seu poder.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:10.64,0:22:13.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Strong Right!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:21.77,0:22:23.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que...?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:44.09,0:22:45.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:48.59,0:22:51.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:57.81,0:22:59.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê...? O que foi aquilo?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:00.71,0:23:04.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah...? Vocês não sabiam?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:05.73,0:23:08.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, então eu vou contar.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:09.57,0:23:12.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou um humano modificado.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:12.82,0:23:14.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um ciborgue!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:24.25,0:23:26.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um dos Chapéus de Palha?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:27.84,0:23:30.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É verdade?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:30.01,0:23:34.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim. Minha própria investigação\Nchegou à mesma conclusão.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:34.01,0:23:37.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acabei de pedir pro Lucci confirmar\Ncom o governo. Então, olha...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:38.94,0:23:45.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É... Quando contatei o governo,\Neles disseram que ela é dos Chapéus de Palha.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:52.91,0:23:59.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então... eles, os Chapéus de Palha,\Nnão têm como se defender.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:59.00,0:24:00.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que diabos?!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:00.84,0:24:03.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É porque a gente não quis consertar o navio deles?!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:03.81,0:24:05.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Difícil dizer.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:05.79,0:24:10.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas independente do motivo,\Na verdade é que temos provas contra eles.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:10.41,0:24:13.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Podemos descobrir o motivo\Ndepois que eles estiverem amarrados.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:13.84,0:24:16.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não sei o que vocês estão pensando,
Dialogue: 5,0:24:16.51,0:24:21.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas vocês vão pagar por isso, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:30.82,0:24:34.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Tem problema!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:34.36,0:24:36.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Você é muito barulhento, Tilestone!\N– Você é muito barulhento, Tilestone!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:36.70,0:24:39.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que falta de educação! Vocês todos, fiquem quietos!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:39.87,0:24:42.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sr. Iceburg!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:42.40,0:24:45.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que bom que você voltou a si!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:47.25,0:24:50.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você grita cada palavra que diz!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:50.76,0:24:52.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Faz mal pra ele, entendeu?!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:52.51,0:24:56.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É! Você tem razão! Desculpa!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:57.30,0:25:00.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é verdade!\NTem problema! Escutem, vocês!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:00.18,0:25:02.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não entrem no quarto.\NFalem de onde estão.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:02.98,0:25:09.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele pirata Chapéu de Palha de ontem\Ncomeçou uma briga com o Franky no Dock One,
Dialogue: 5,0:25:09.23,0:25:12.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e estão destruindo o estaleiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:16.53,0:25:18.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha...
Dialogue: 5,0:25:18.62,0:25:20.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sr. Iceburg!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:23.16,0:25:28.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele desgraçado...! Ele tem muita coragem\Nde aparecer no dock!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:31.46,0:25:35.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, descanse, Sr. Iceburg.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:36.97,0:25:40.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu estarei aqui ao seu lado.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:49.52,0:25:51.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:57.07,0:25:59.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cuidado! Tá caindo!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:59.24,0:26:02.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O navio tá se despedaçando!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:02.41,0:26:05.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parem! Essa luta é uma loucura!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:10.21,0:26:14.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Acaba com esse idiota de biquíni!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:14.09,0:26:15.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mano!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:15.72,0:26:18.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dá uma boa luta nele!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:25.60,0:26:29.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, seu traseiro... já era!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:32.23,0:26:37.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então chuta se conseguir!\NSeus ataques não funcionam contra mim!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:47.46,0:26:50.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:54.46,0:26:55.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 5,0:26:55.89,0:26:57.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Whip!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:06.39,0:27:09.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que isso?! O que aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:09.89,0:27:11.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! Aquele é...!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:13.48,0:27:14.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem foi?!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:20.16,0:27:26.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês tem muita cara de pau!\NQual é o seu objetivo, Chapéu de Palha?!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:33.38,0:27:36.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Galley-La... O que vocês querem?
Dialogue: 5,0:27:38.51,0:27:42.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São os encarregados do Dock One!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:53.10,0:27:57.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza! Os encarregados finalmente chegaram!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:57.07,0:28:01.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa foi por pouco! O estaleiro\Ntá praticamente destruído!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:01.78,0:28:05.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ainda bem! São os carpinteiros\Nque conhecemos ontem!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:05.53,0:28:07.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles estão do nosso lado, certo?
Dialogue: 5,0:28:07.08,0:28:10.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, seus fanfarrões da Galley-La!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:10.04,0:28:13.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês não deviam se meter na nossa luta!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:13.46,0:28:15.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Querem se machucar?
Dialogue: 5,0:28:15.34,0:28:17.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olha quem fala.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:17.71,0:28:23.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Destruir nossa fábrica é motivo suficiente\Npra fazer vocês pagarem o preço!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:23.34,0:28:28.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tem razão, Franky!\NComo vai resolver isso?!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:28.11,0:28:32.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Calma, Tilestone.\NA gente fala disso depois.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:32.69,0:28:36.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Temos assuntos mais importantes agora.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:37.61,0:28:40.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo, Chapéu de Palha Luffy?
Dialogue: 5,0:28:40.53,0:28:42.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você sabe do que eu tô falando.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:42.40,0:28:45.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tô surpreso que apareceu aqui de novo.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:45.24,0:28:49.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? Por quê? A gente veio aqui porque\Nouviu as notícias sobre o Icechefe.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:51.00,0:28:56.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, minha família não bastou,\Nentão mexeu com a Galley-La também?
Dialogue: 5,0:28:56.46,0:29:00.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês são moleques que irritam\Ntodo mundo que encontram pela frente?!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:00.96,0:29:04.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como eu disse, a gente não fez nada!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:04.55,0:29:08.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Finge que não sabe,\Ne a gente aperta o cerco!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:08.51,0:29:12.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rope Action Half-Knot!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:13.94,0:29:16.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não consigo respirar... Não consigo respirar...!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:17.61,0:29:20.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Air... Drive!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:23.53,0:29:28.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seus filhos da mãe! Vocês não sabem\No que significa 'não se meter'?!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:28.03,0:29:31.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu é que tenho uma pendência com ele!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:35.21,0:29:36.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Coo coo!}
Dialogue: 5,0:29:36.46,0:29:39.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dá uma surra neles, Galley-La Company!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:39.30,0:29:41.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os cinco furiosos da empresa estão lutando!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:41.84,0:29:45.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera, o quê? Por que os carpinteiros\Nestão lutando contra a gente também?!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:45.47,0:29:47.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá esquentando.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:50.14,0:29:55.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Espera! Eu não tenho o menor\Nmotivo pra lutar contra vocês!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:00.19,0:30:03.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tem... poderes de Akuma no Mi?
Dialogue: 5,0:30:14.66,0:30:18.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, vocês desgraçados estão ouvindo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:20.34,0:30:22.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu disse...
Dialogue: 5,0:30:24.80,0:30:28.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,que ele é a minha presa!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:31.80,0:30:33.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:30:35.35,0:30:38.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não temos tempo pra perder com você, Franky!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:38.98,0:30:42.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você disse, macaco selvagem?!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:42.61,0:30:46.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem tá se metendo é você, Franky!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:50.03,0:30:54.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é o nosso Tilestone! Forte como sempre!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:02.25,0:31:05.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Coo coo! Coo coo!}
Dialogue: 5,0:31:09.68,0:31:12.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu idiota! Para com isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:29.24,0:31:31.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esses caras são durões!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:31.20,0:31:34.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Qual é a de vocês?!\NPelo menos me digam por que estão fazendo isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:40.29,0:31:44.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha, nós é que\Ngostaríamos de saber o porquê.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:46.71,0:31:53.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ontem à noite, invasores entraram no escritório\Ne atacaram o Sr. Iceburg.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:53.01,0:31:54.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Foram vocês! Admitam!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:54.64,0:31:58.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser... Isso não pode ser...
Dialogue: 5,0:31:58.06,0:32:00.77,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles se meteram na minha luta de qualquer jeito.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:23.42,0:32:28.34,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquela era... sem dúvida, Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:28.34,0:32:32.63,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele homem grande que estava com ela\Ntambém era um dos Chapéus de Palha?
Dialogue: 5,0:32:32.63,0:32:36.69,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que eles me atacaram?
Dialogue: 5,0:32:36.69,0:32:40.06,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,É difícil imaginar que fizeram\Nisso como vingança por ontem.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:40.06,0:32:43.27,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles devem estar atrás de algo meu.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:43.27,0:32:47.69,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, esses piratas são\Nligados ao governo?
Dialogue: 5,0:32:47.69,0:32:50.53,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ou será que eles realmente estão atrás de...?
Dialogue: 5,0:32:52.49,0:32:54.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha...
Dialogue: 5,0:32:55.66,0:32:58.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Notícia de última hora! Última hora!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:58.24,0:33:02.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pelo que o Prefeito Iceburg disse,\Nos culpados foram identificados!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:02.41,0:33:03.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! É verdade?!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:03.92,0:33:07.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Avisem a cidade inteira imediatamente\Ne encurralen os desgraçados!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:07.46,0:33:10.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não deixem eles saírem de Water Seven!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:10.39,0:33:12.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capturem eles!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:13.93,0:33:16.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os culpados que atacaram o Sr. Iceburg são...
Dialogue: 5,0:33:19.81,0:33:23.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,os Piratas do Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:26.73,0:33:30.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Iceburg foi atacado?\NDo que vocês estão falando?
Dialogue: 5,0:33:34.03,0:33:36.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Q-Que que eles querem dizer?
Dialogue: 5,0:33:38.45,0:33:43.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,N... Não seja ridículo! Por que...\NPor que a gente faria uma coisa dessas?!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:43.66,0:33:50.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando o Sr. Iceburg acordou, ele nos disse\Nque se lembrava dos dois que fizeram isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:50.46,0:33:53.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um era um homem grande usando uma máscara.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:53.97,0:33:57.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O outro era uma mulher alta.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:57.18,0:34:03.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando perguntamos ao governo,\Neles confirmaram a ligação dela com vocês:
Dialogue: 5,0:34:03.93,0:34:06.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nico Robin, a mulher\Ncom uma recompensa pela cabeça!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:08.06,0:34:09.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin?!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:13.82,0:34:19.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês vieram pra essa ilha como\Nparte de um plano pra matar o Sr. Iceburg?
Dialogue: 5,0:34:19.28,0:34:24.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ou decidiram fazer isso\Ndepois que o conheceram ontem?
Dialogue: 5,0:34:24.70,0:34:28.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não sei como vocês piratas pensam...
Dialogue: 5,0:34:29.04,0:34:33.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas já que sabemos que são culpados,\Nnão tem como deixar vocês livres.
Dialogue: 5,0:34:33.59,0:34:36.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então ele é um dos culpados?
Dialogue: 5,0:34:36.01,0:34:38.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos fazer ele pagar! Temos que fazer!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:38.63,0:34:39.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, não!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:39.76,0:34:43.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, então o Iceburg morreu ou não?
Dialogue: 5,0:34:43.68,0:34:47.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como se um bando de idiotas pudesse matá-lo.
Dialogue: 5,0:34:47.64,0:34:53.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Enquanto esse desgraçado viver,\Nele pode ir atrás do Sr. Iceburg de novo.
Dialogue: 5,0:34:53.61,0:34:56.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então vamos cuidar dele aqui e agora.
Dialogue: 5,0:34:59.91,0:35:02.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqui diz "vivo ou morto".
Dialogue: 5,0:35:02.24,0:35:04.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles te querem de qualquer jeito.
Dialogue: 5,0:35:04.91,0:35:07.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você sabe o que significa\Nser um homem procurado?
Dialogue: 5,0:35:07.79,0:35:12.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês piratas não podem reclamar,\Nnão importa quem faça o que com vocês.
Dialogue: 5,0:35:12.63,0:35:16.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Em outras palavras, as leis do mundo\Nnão protegem vocês.
Dialogue: 5,0:35:17.13,0:35:18.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:35:19.72,0:35:22.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nós somos fora da lei.
Dialogue: 5,0:35:22.89,0:35:25.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sei disso. Mas...
Dialogue: 5,0:35:25.68,0:35:31.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,não fale mal da Robin\Nsem saber nada sobre ela!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:31.15,0:35:32.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 5,0:35:32.86,0:35:34.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me deixa ver o Icechefe!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:34.77,0:35:37.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenho certeza que ele tá enganado!\NNão tem como ter sido a Robin!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:37.82,0:35:42.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que deixaríamos você se aproximar\Nquando não sabemos suas intenções?!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:43.49,0:35:46.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tem razão! Amarrem eles!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:46.49,0:35:49.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles tentaram matar nosso herói!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:49.37,0:35:51.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mandem eles pra forca!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:51.87,0:35:55.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ei! O que vocês estão dizendo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:55.10,0:35:57.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sua vadia!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:57.51,0:36:01.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Você estava com aquele\NCha-péu de Palha antes, não é?
Dialogue: 5,0:36:01.59,0:36:03.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você deve ser uma deles também!
Dialogue: 5,0:36:03.43,0:36:04.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é?!
Dialogue: 5,0:36:04.71,0:36:08.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, ele tem razão! Eu vi ela também!
Dialogue: 5,0:36:08.45,0:36:10.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não vamos deixar vocês fugirem!
Dialogue: 5,0:36:10.18,0:36:12.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parem de resistir!
Dialogue: 5,0:36:12.79,0:36:14.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, para com isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:36:15.40,0:36:16.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 5,0:36:17.11,0:36:20.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A notícia já tá se espalhando\Npela cidade.
Dialogue: 5,0:36:20.36,0:36:22.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês não têm pra onde fugir!
Dialogue: 5,0:36:22.88,0:36:26.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos derrubar cada um de vocês!
Dialogue: 5,0:36:26.45,0:36:28.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Extra! Extra!
Dialogue: 5,0:36:28.66,0:36:34.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os Piratas do Chapéu de Palha são os principais suspeitos\Nda tentativa de assassinato do Sr. Iceburg!
Dialogue: 5,0:36:34.42,0:36:40.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nós do Sentinela de Hydro City pagaremos por qualquer\Ninformação sobre o paradeiro deles!
Dialogue: 5,0:36:42.13,0:36:44.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os culpados estão nessa ilha!
Dialogue: 5,0:36:46.39,0:36:51.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Encontrem os Chapéus de Palha\Ne mandem todos pra forca!
Dialogue: 5,0:36:51.93,0:36:54.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso!
